author: desmoinesregister.com
title: Hy-Vee Big Four Classic tickets available Oct. 30
text:
File photo (Photo: The Register)
Tickets for the Big Four Classic go on sale to the public on Oct. 30.
The state’s four NCAA Division I men’s basketball teams will be in action in the same venue for the fourth consecutive year at Wells Fargo Arena on Dec. 19.
The first game of the doubleheader will feature Drake and Iowa beginning at 3:30 p.m. The game will be broadcast on ESPN3.com. Iowa State and UNI will play the second game at 6 p.m., with the game being broadcast on ESPNU.
Tickets, which range in price from $25-70, go on sale Oct. 30 at 10 a.m. exclusively through the Wells Fargo Arena Box Office, Hy-VeeTix.com, 844-55-HYVEE, or 22 Hy-Vee Stores in Des Moines and Ames. Tickets are good for admission to both games of the doubleheader.
